| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5540 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 10c9b7f4-d524-50e7-8b5e-7aeea40c3065"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
